'''''Rebecca''''' ni filime yo muri [[Gana]]-[[Nijeriya]] 2016 iyobowe na Shirley Frimpong-Manso, ikinwamo na Yvonne Okoro na Joseph Benjamin<ref>Rebecca (2016) - Filmaffinity <nowiki>https://www.filmaffinity.com</nowiki> › film390520</ref> . Nk’uko Manso abitangaza ngo iyi filime yasohotse bwa mbere i Londres, mbere ya [[Gana]] kubera ubukungu bw'igihugu bigatuma igabanuka ry'abakunzi ba filime<ref>Rebecca Movie - Sparrow Productions <nowiki>http://sparrowproductions.net</nowiki> › rebecca</ref>. Iyi filime ni filime ya kabiri yakinnye igaragaramo umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri [[Nijeriya]] Yvonne Okoro<ref>REBECCA | African Movie Review <nowiki>https://www.talkafricanmovies.com</nowiki> › Home › REBECCA</ref>. 

== Abakinnyi ==

* Joseph Benjamin nka Clifford
* Yvonne Okoro nka Rebecca

== Umugambi ==
Filime itangirana na Clifford ( Joseph Benjamin ) na Rebecca ( Yvonne Okoro ) bazimiye mu ishyamba nyuma yuko imodoka yabo isabye gusanwa<ref>Rebecca - Nollywood Reinvented <nowiki>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com</nowiki> › 2016/10 › reb...</ref>. Byagaragaye ko Rebecca yasezeranijwe na Clifford kuva mu bwana bwabo ko bazabana<ref>Rebecca (film del 2016) <nowiki>https://it.hrvwiki.net</nowiki> › wiki › Rebecc...</ref>. Mu gihe Rebecca yacecetse mu rugendo rwose kandi asa nkaho atababajwe n'amagambo yavuzwe n'umugabo we mushya<ref>rebecca - Ghana Film Industry <nowiki>https://www.ghanafilmindustry.com</nowiki> › tag › rebecca</ref>, Clifford agaragaza ko adashaka gushyingiranwa nawe neza kuko yashakaga gusohoza icyifuzo cye cyo gupfa kwa se<ref>“ Rebecca ” Shirley's Two-Cast Film, to be Premiered in ... (ghanafilmindustry.com)</ref>. Clifford yarumwe nikiremwa cyomwishyamba kandi ibi biganisha kubiganiro byambere hagati yabo. Rebecca amufasha gukira igikomere cye. Aramuhishurira kandi ko mbere yakundaga kandi akagaragaza ko atamwitayeho kubera ko atamwubaha kandi ko amukunda<ref>Shirley Frimpong-Manso's 'Rebecca' Movie Saves The Day At ... <nowiki>https://www.peacefmonline.com</nowiki> › movies › 201603</ref>. Nyuma y'ibiganiro birebire hagati yabo, batangiye gukundana. Rebecca ashimuswe nabagabo babiri, nyuma byaje kugaragara ko byateguwe  nuwahoze ari umukunzi we<ref>20 Best Ghanaian Movies Every Ghallywood Fan Should Watch <nowiki>https://www.wiki.ng</nowiki> › wiki › 2021-20-best-ghanaian-m...</ref>. Rebecca asubira kwa Clifford maze asobanura imigambi ye yose yo guhimbira urupfu rwe no guhagarika umushoferi we kumukurikira amuroga. Nyuma yo kumva no kubona ukuri kwinginga kwe, Clifford aramwakira mugihe bombi bategereje itsinda ryabatabazi<ref>Yvonne Okoro, Biography - GhanaWeb <nowiki>https://www.ghanaweb.com</nowiki> › person › Yvonne-Okoro-...</ref>.
